attributeSource.infoString2: THE SPENCER GROUP RE AND AUCTION

data.description: This charming brick ranch, recently updated and situated on 2.5 acres near Bassett Forks, is a true gem. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, a large family room, and spacious kitchen, this home offers both comfort and style. A new bathroom and laundry room have been added to the basement, enhancing its functionality. Beyond the visible upgrades, the home is equipped with additional features that contribute to its overall appeal. Three years ago, spray foam insulation was installed, ensuring a more energy-efficient utility bill. The main water line was replaced just two years ago, and the house comes with a security system and a smart thermostat with room sensors for added convenience. Moreover, this charming property is conveniently located just minutes away from shopping and restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to experience the beauty of this home; schedule your appointment today.
